Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:07.68,Background,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.32,Background,,0,0,0,,More! Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no different than being in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to stay in the same place as the Judo and Tennis Clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom made the reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that. Let's take a swim in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the pool after I take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Maybe it's because his father{uncle} has postponed coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,His father{uncle} was supposed to come with us on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan is quite naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at a resort. It'd be a drag if I had a chaperone with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to enjoy this summer without my father as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Teenage summer. A wild{as in wild life} summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is better than swimsuits in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hot girl. A good chance for a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got gorgeous boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's slender, and her figure's good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like I did when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be trying to recover from a break-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have something in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite an elegant garden and building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose carefully, as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This guest house{he's saying it in japanese} is popular among commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You should call it a "pension."{in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, cancel my reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Would you like to go back to your{parents} villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's in her swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Young master, you are drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Young master, your nose is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed the Tennis Club, and I get to see Narusawa Yui. This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't photograph Yui-san's sacred figure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in her swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Kondou Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he here too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beige?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?{2, 26:19}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, beige.{ep 2 26:22}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat!{ep 02 26：23}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to lie on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bumping into me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in some old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know nothing about women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want to hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on and try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't hit a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Women aren't always weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to make a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite sport?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite sport is sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about tennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Penis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A joke, just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll play a match with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Onii-chan? Why are you shouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Onii-chan do something rude to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to play a tennis match against your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A tennis match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't follow me around like a chaperone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother is short-tempered. That was harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. He's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm going to play a match against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat the crap out of Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a three-set match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use a tie-break system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tanaka Misa. I'm going to beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kondou Makoto. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her real underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This stinks of sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. I used it to wipe my sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I lost, let me treat you to lunch.{dinner?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Western? Japanese? Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hungry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go to that amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's shower off and meet here again in twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be late. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, why don't you go swimming as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've been in a real summer mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, that's alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:00.26,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Sign: Drinking under 20 is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Yui-san's elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yui-san's classmate.\N My name is Saionji Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that Yui-san had such a beautiful sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a villa near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have dinner with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san can come too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice. Right, Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really don't like roller coasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A little misunderstanding,\N a casual remark...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get over this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So your boyfriend looks like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a coincidence that we met here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps... it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be waiting in my room with a bottle of champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope dinner will be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can bring your sister too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot Misako-san was here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They both went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:17.77,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Note: We were invited to Saionji's villa. Why don't you come join us? (Yui is with me.) Misako
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They went to Aritomo's villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can enjoy our dinner all by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a splendid dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We{My parents} recruited a master chef from the Grand Imperial Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this young lady to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She just drank something unfamiliar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was Yui-san's first time drinking alcohol. Unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Misako-san, the stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you around the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be a lovely night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A lovely night... Her smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be...{an opportunity}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are {\i1}you{\i0\fscx150} {\r}here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he is a classmate of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and is willing to take a\N commemorative photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Dinner is over? I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, why don't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attitude and words
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are rather harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:46.61,Background,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great. I get to see Yui-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You took that photo of Yui and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is Yui-chan asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sleeping face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiki-kun, I'm going to show Yui-san's sister around the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So could you leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty. Mom, I want some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Yui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, water...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go get some yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Men don't like drunk girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? He's confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I should snap Yui-chan's sleeping face now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A good chance for a photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Yui's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was kind of a city boy, but he's rather wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wild men...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a wild guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't believe I can see so many stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are as many stars as there are people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And every person is one of those stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is my star?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, when's your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,March 29th.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aries. Our affinity should be pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,November 27th, Sagittarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your ex-boyfriend?{he didn't say ex before but he says ex here}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you two should've gotten along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm the substitute for this boyfriend who looks like me and should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,very compatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop treating me like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,First you're sulky, then you get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Men who don't understand\N women's feelings are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not beige.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not wearing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you were at the amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You were already interested in me at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pendant is hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost to you in the tennis match,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll be your slave today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then kneel before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bigger than your ex's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean. Don't talk about my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That feels good, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me look at yours this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only done this with one other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gentle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never experienced anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm coming. I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. On, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a safe day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go to the pool and take a swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have another round?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you not to return to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't your sister worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a nice sister. She cares about her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She just lives with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So she loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Misa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? I heard that you were at this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Misa! It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa! Hey, Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is how my summer love affair ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.93,0:24:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.22,0:24:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, Yui is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.76,0:24:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you'll annoy everyone else if you stay inside the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.37,0:24:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.88,0:24:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I'll treat you to taiyaki{fish-shaped pancake filled with bean jam} afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.88,0:24:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Note: Taiyaki are fish-shaped pancakes filled with bean jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.60,0:25:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me so nicely, and what did I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A paper airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.73,0:25:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... Isn't this a prescription?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasohachi Community Hospital. Sugimoto Sakurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.33,0:25:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.77,0:25:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.57,0:25:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Turbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to catch a cold,\N so I'll close the window, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.15,0:25:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.21,0:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard a bird chirp.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.87,0:25:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.15,0:25:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.09,0:26:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.36,0:26:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were late, I caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.29,0:26:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.89,0:26:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.11,0:26:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.03,0:26:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's already autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.48,0:26:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)\fnArtificeSSK\bord0\fs28\pos(449,416)\c&H9D4F3A&\be1}To be continued...
