Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.60,0:27:05.60,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Showered by a sudden rain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.85,0:27:09.73,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}kasa mo sasazu ni aruita ra
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.85,0:27:09.73,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Walking without putting up my umbrella
