Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.15,0:27:17.15,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}People in the street looked at me strangely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.12,0:27:27.25,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}mada haru asai san gatsu no gogo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.25,0:27:31.54,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}tsumetai ame no sora miage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.12,0:27:27.25,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}On an early spring afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.25,0:27:31.54,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I looked up at the sky in the cold rain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:38.59,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}odoritaku naru youna kibun de aruita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:38.59,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I walked with an urge to dance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.51,0:27:53.11,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}arifureta nichijyou ni itsuka kokoro ga kumotte ta
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.51,0:27:53.11,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}My heart was clouded by the familiar days
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.11,0:28:00.70,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}sonna koto sae kizukazu ni ita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.11,0:28:00.70,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I didn't understand anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.61,0:28:04.62,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.61,0:28:04.62,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.95,0:28:14.96,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}honno sasayakana nandemo nai youna yuuki dakeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.95,0:28:14.96,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}It was a small piece of courage, almost like nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.96,0:28:22.18,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}sonna koto de naze ka sukoshi kokoro ga hareta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.96,0:28:22.18,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I don't know why, but it brightened my heart a bit
